    <node id="Contracting officer">
      <data key="d0">Contracting officer</data>
      <data key="d3">doc-8307fa18b297b3e4ece0b76bb0b726f3-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-3c8658f6ff895cbdf8dd72df8a08f90f-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-cfcf172eeeeba354449b6cf11d6acc94-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-216ef3624588c4d8ba2f0a7d927a0c70-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-a4fb44a50472ca98bb40f038cdaffc48-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-06db059943ebc243f385e13bac5ffcda-chunk-000</data>
      <data key="d2">Agency heads designate the contracting officer as the source selection authority.&lt;SEP&gt;Individual responsible for the exchange of information with potential offerors.&lt;SEP&gt;A person responsible for listing attachments in Section J.</data>
      <data key="d1">other</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1782211793</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Government">
      <data key="d0">Government</data>
      <data key="d3">doc-bbf1cc688706dd430bfe505423cb9745-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-3c8658f6ff895cbdf8dd72df8a08f90f-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-db49040870203ca440941cb0a7037ccf-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-cfcf172eeeeba354449b6cf11d6acc94-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-8d0d7e22b7e4569d562e86ab0038c0aa-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-ad72395f3b32d9bfb15e688edd27ebbe-chunk-000</data>
      <data key="d2">When it may be in the best interest of the Government to consider award to other than the lowest priced offeror or other than the highest technically rated offeror.&lt;SEP&gt;When using a tradeoff process, the Government may consider factors other than cost or price.&lt;SEP&gt;The perceived benefits of the higher priced proposal shall merit the additional cost.&lt;SEP&gt;Allows the Government to accept other than the lowest priced proposal.&lt;SEP&gt;Government entity responsible for publicizing requirements and soliciting information.&lt;SEP&gt;Companies, institutions, government bodies, groups that participate in oral presentations and make source selection decisions.</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1782212206</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
