      <data key="d2">The solicitation shall state whether all evaluation factors other than cost or price, when combined, are significantly more important than, approximately equal to, or significantly less important than cost or price.&lt;SEP&gt;All evaluation factors and significant subfactors that will affect contract award and their relative importance shall be clearly stated in the solicitation.</data>
