      <data key="d2">Letter RFPs may be used in sole source acquisitions and other appropriate circumstances.&lt;SEP&gt;A solicitation method that should be as complete as possible and include specific details such as RFP number and date, contracting officer's contact information, type of contract, quantity and description of items, delivery dates, certifications, contract terms, instructions to offerors, evaluation criteria, proposal due date, and other relevant information.&lt;SEP&gt;A solicitation method that should be as complete as possible and include specific details such as RFP number and date, contracting officer's contact information, type of contract, quantity&lt;SEP&gt;A solicitation method used in sole source acquisitions and other appropriate circumstances, not relieving the contracting officer from complying with other FAR requirements.</data>
      <data key="d1">other</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1782211695</data>
