    <node id="Competitive Range">
      <data key="d0">Competitive Range</data>
      <data key="d3">doc-57fca498e8ef8f0c8e2675ed4ea878f1-chunk-000</data>
      <data key="d2">The adverse past performance information is addressed and evaluated to determine if a proposal should be placed in the competitive range.</data>
      <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1782211946</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Offeror">
      <data key="d0">Offeror</data>
      <data key="d3">doc-57fca498e8ef8f0c8e2675ed4ea878f1-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-06db059943ebc243f385e13bac5ffcda-chunk-000</data>
      <data key="d2">The adverse past performance information is addressed and evaluated, and may be considered in rating proposals for the purpose of establishing the competitive range.&lt;SEP&gt;The adverse past performance information to which the offeror has not previously had an opportunity to comment.</data>
      <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1782211947</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Proposal Deficiencies, Material Omissions, Technical or Cost Elements">
      <data key="d0">Proposal Deficiencies, Material Omissions, Technical or Cost Elements</data>
      <data key="d3">doc-57fca498e8ef8f0c8e2675ed4ea878f1-chunk-000</data>
      <data key="d2">Such communications shall not be used to cure proposal deficiencies or material omissions, materially alter the technical or cost elements of the proposal, and/or otherwise revise the proposal.&lt;SEP&gt;Such communications may be used to enhance Government understanding of proposals, allow reasonable interpretation of the proposal, or facilitate the Government’s evaluation process.&lt;SEP&gt;Such communications may be considered in rating proposals for the purpose of establishing the competitive range.</data>
      <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1782211996</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Deficiency">
      <data key="d0">Deficiency</data>
      <data key="d1">other</data>
      <data key="d2">A material failure of a proposal to meet a Government requirement or a combination of significant weaknesses in a proposal that increases the risk of unsuccessful contract performance to an unacceptable level.</data>
      <data key="d3">doc-ce6df67b501cc65b8bf112bed214d0a5-chunk-000</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1782211996</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Proposal Interpretation">
      <data key="d0">Proposal Interpretation</data>
      <data key="d3">doc-57fca498e8ef8f0c8e2675ed4ea878f1-chunk-000</data>
      <data key="d2">Such communications may be used to enhance Government understanding of proposals, allow reasonable interpretation of the proposal, or facilitate the Government’s evaluation process.&lt;SEP&gt;Such communications may be used to address ambiguities in the proposal or other concerns (e.g., perceived deficiencies, weaknesses, errors, omissions, or mistakes).</data>
      <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1782211996</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Proposal revision">
      <data key="d0">Proposal revision</data>
      <data key="d3">doc-ce6df67b501cc65b8bf112bed214d0a5-chunk-000</data>
      <data key="d2">A "significant weakness" in the proposal is a flaw that appreciably increases the risk of unsuccessful contract performance.</data>
      <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1782211996</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
