      <data key="d3">doc-ce6df67b501cc65b8bf112bed214d0a5-chunk-000</data>
      <data key="d2">A proposal modification is a change made to a proposal before the solicitation closing date and time, or made in response to an amendment, or made to correct a mistake at any time before award.</data>
      <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
