    <node id="Proposal evaluation">
      <data key="d0">Proposal evaluation</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">An assessment of the proposal and the offeror’s ability to perform the prospective contract successfully, conducted by an agency to evaluate competitive proposals and assess their relative qualities based on specified factors and subfactors, using various rating methods or combinations thereof, and documenting the relative strengths, deficiencies, significant weaknesses, and risks in the contract file.</data>
      <data key="d3">doc-6ea357fd59c34d4f9c7984ccfcb4ad4c-chunk-000</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1782212698</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Cost or price evaluation">
      <data key="d0">Cost or price evaluation</data>
      <data key="d3">doc-6ea357fd59c34d4f9c7984ccfcb4ad4c-chunk-000</data>
      <data key="d2">Proposal evaluation includes the cost or price evaluation as one of its components, which normally establishes price reasonableness and may include a cost analysis in limited situations to establish the reasonableness of the offeror's price.</data>
      <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1782212698</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
