      <data key="d7">1.0</data>
      <data key="d8">When oral presentations are required, the solicitation shall provide offerors with sufficient information to prepare them, and contracting officers should also consider alternatives to on-site oral presentations (e.g., teleconferencing, video teleconferencing).</data>
