    <edge source="RFPs" target="Letter RFPs">
      <data key="d7">10.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Letter RFPs may be used in certain circumstances where RFPs are not required.&lt;SEP&gt;Letter RFPs may be used in certain situations where RFPs are not required.&lt;SEP&gt;Letter RFPs and RFPs are different types of requests for proposals.&lt;SEP&gt;Letter RFPs do not require the same level of compliance as RFPs.</data>
